# Agent files under agents/generated/ are emitted by `guild generate`
# from panel.manifest.toml + tools-map.toml + the source fragments.
# Marking them linguist-generated collapses them in GitHub diffs and
# excludes them from language stats — they are output, not source.
# Regenerate with `guild generate`; do not hand-edit. The freshness
# test (generated-panel.test.ts) fails if the committed tree drifts
# from a fresh regen.
agents/generated/** linguist-generated=true
